how to run 

1) change the path for storing the iso file in command make mykernel.iso in make file 
grub-mkrescue --output=/home/aditya/Downloads/build/mykernel.iso iso

2) start virtual box 

3) make a virtual machine having type as other and type as other/unknown and name as My Operating System

4) memory size 32 mb

5) hard disk select- not add a virtual hard disk

6) open terminal type 
	1) make clean
	2) make run 
	3) virtual machine will run (locate the mykernel.iso file (for the first time))
